      "comment": "STILL BELIEVE (8) had been racing in honest fashion recording two placings in a row before finishing fifth (27.03) at Ballarat latest. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from three starts. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. MAGIZOOLOGIST (4) missed the frame last time but had been racing well prior to that, winning a T3 RSTW three back before a placing at this track the following run. Expecting significant improvement. ASTON POSEIDON (2) placed last time (24.57) at Bendigo in a T3 RSTW, finishing second and beaten 8 lengths. Has already won out of this draw. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. RUGRAT TOMMY (7) is worth consideration.",
